\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
\lambda_{1}\mathbf{v}_{1}+...+\lambda_{n}\mathbf{v}_{n}=0.\label{eq:linear dependence}\end{equation}

\end_inset

If no such numbers exist, i.e.\InsetSpace ~
if Eq.\InsetSpace ~
(
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq:linear dependence}

\end_inset

