\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z$
\end_inset

 that satisfy 
\begin_inset Formula $x=-\frac{b}{a}y-\frac{c}{a}z$
\end_inset

.
 Hence, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}=y\mathbf{e}_{1}+z\mathbf{e}_{2}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

