\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 exists.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subparagraph
Answer:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The inverse operator exists only if 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{f}^{*}(\mathbf{u})\neq-1$
\end_inset

: then 
