\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{a},\mathbf{b}$
\end_inset

.
 (The proof of the Statement above does not use the fact that the space
 is 
\emph on
three
\emph default
-dimen\SpecialChar \-
sion\SpecialChar \-
al!) We may then regard these 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}n(n-1)$
\end_inset

