\emph on
orientation
\emph default
 of the parallelogram in the 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-dimen\SpecialChar \-
sion\SpecialChar \-
al space.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We arrived at the idea that the oriented area of the parallelogram spanned
