\begin_layout Paragraph
Statement:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Any 
\begin_inset Formula $(N-1)$
\end_inset

-vector in an 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

-dimen\SpecialChar \-
sion\SpecialChar \-
al space can be written as a single-term exterior product of the
