\end_inset

 can be uniquely characterized by a nonzero tensor such as 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}_{1}\wedge...\wedge\mathbf{v}_{k}$
\end_inset

 in which the constituents --- the vectors 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}_{1}$
\end_inset

,..., 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}_{k}$
\end_inset

