\begin_inset Formula $q_{1}(\hat{A})=\textrm{Tr}\hat{A}$
\end_inset

.
 More compactly, the statement can be written as
\begin_inset Formula \[
Q_{\hat{A}}\left(\lambda\right)\hat{1}_{\wedge^{N}V}=\sum_{k=0}^{N}\left(-\lambda\right)^{N-k}(\wedge^{N}\hat{A}^{k}).\]

\end_inset


