\begin_inset Formula $\textrm{End}(\wedge^{k}V)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\textrm{End}(\wedge^{N-k}V)$
\end_inset

 are canonically isomorphic (
\begin_inset Formula $1\leq k<N$
\end_inset

).
 Specifically, if 
