\begin_inset Formula \[
\hat{P}_{\lambda_{0}}=\sum_{k=1}^{n}\left[\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}c_{k}q_{k+i}(-\hat{A})^{i}+\sum_{i=n}^{N-k}c_{k}q_{k+i}(-\hat{A})^{i}\right].\]

\end_inset

The first sum yields 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{1}$
\end_inset

 by Eq.\InsetSpace ~
(
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq:ck condition}

\end_inset

), and so we obtain Eq.\InsetSpace ~
(
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{eq:projector jordan cell general}

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

