\begin_inset Formula \[
\hat{A}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 1\\
0 & 0\end{array}\right)=\mathbf{e}_{1}\otimes\mathbf{e}_{2}^{*}.\]

\end_inset

This operator has a Jordan cell with eigenvalue 0 spanned by the basis vectors
 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{e}_{1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{e}_{2}$
\end_inset

.
