\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{e}_{1}$
\end_inset

, and a possible projector onto this eigenvector is 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{P}=\mathbf{e}_{1}\otimes\mathbf{e}_{1}^{*}$
\end_inset

.
