 It is easy to guess the eigenvectors, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}_{1}=\underbar{1}$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=0$
\end_inset

) and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}_{2}=\underbar{x}$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=1)$
\end_inset

