\begin_layout Paragraph
Exercise 5:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Consider the orthogonal transformations 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{R}_{\alpha}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{M}_{\mathbf{n}}$
\end_inset

 and an orthonormal basis 
